---
title: Serrano, Parmigiano and Parma Ham Filled Pasta with Veggie 'Nduja Sauce and Rocket
description: Featuring a hot, umami blend of Calabrian chillies and peppers, this 'Nduja is completely meat-free but with all the same flavour. It pairs perfectly with the creamy filling of our Parmigiano Reggiano and Parma ham filled pasta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R25_W27_UK_QR21416-3_Main_high-31edaea3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66b48999edc49d29cccc645b-en-GB.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 15 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 482 kcal
  fat: 17.7 g
  saturated fat: 8.9 g
  carbohydrates: 54.2 g
